{"tid":2412011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登政府將於月底前支付2億美元於世衞以表示支持","createTime":"2021-02-17T18:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T18:44:57.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"21c776fba36c69a54bed4182af0a3d8cbb2a0aff","tid":2412011,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"（中央社紐約聯合國總部17日綜合外電報導）美國國務卿布林肯今天表示，在新政府推翻前朝退出世界衛生組織（WHO）的計畫後，美國將於月底前支付逾2億美元（約新台幣56億元）的款項給世衛組織。<br />\n<br />\n美國一直是世衛最大金援國，上述款項為美國之前已對世衛承諾的金額。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，布林肯（Antony Blinken）今天在聯合國安全理事會（UN Security Council）一場2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）視訊會議上表示：「這是我國履行作為世衛成員國財務義務的重要一步，同時反映我國重新承諾將確保世衛獲得必要支持，以領導全球回應這場疾病大流行。」<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202102180002.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202102180002.aspx&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOkBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=7fb14e82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202102180002.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"0e56ea75ce6aad10a43976512d15ba843242c2b3","tid":2412011,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T18:07:26.000Z","msg":"若然屬實 譚生菜或會成為最後贏家"},{"pid":"d9d86464c0d82da4191dbd65343b383f346342df","tid":2412011,"uid":89182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T18:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pMOZoqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMOZoqz.jpg&h=67325e5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c7fb22bfb8d612b38b8f41af4dc2016bf057fa8","tid":2412011,"uid":343712,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T18:09:15.000Z","msg":"比錢但無權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a2c68a890f23aef4ea1c50af9b89e77ba24b0b","tid":2412011,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T18:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />